# Context vs Content (Platform UI lock)

- **Workspace Switcher = Context** — show the Workspace name once (full label, never truncated).
- **Page Header / Landing title = Content** — name the work on this screen (e.g. ภาพรวม, จัดซื้อ, สูตร).
- Do **not** repeat the Workspace label in the Header when the Switcher is visible.
- Context and Content must have distinct jobs on every screen.

